{"tid":667933,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【賤嘴無極限】《死侍2》優先場票房輕鬆過200萬","createTime":"2018-05-17T07:27:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T07:27:55.000Z","uid":10958,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dd6a1e78ec8cdd7d39c78eb18400db64aa1384bf","tid":667933,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T07:27:55.000Z","msg":"<strong>【賤嘴無極限】《死侍2》優先場票房輕鬆過200萬</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NretMCzkILNajrMdj9GPnw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20180517f115804.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FNretMCzkILNajrMdj9GPnw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20180517f115804.jpg&h=8fd0b0cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】一般的超級英雄電影，風格都好正經及沉重，但《死侍》(Deadpool)就偏偏反其道而行，風格抵死幽默，亦因此而成功殺出一條新血路，大受觀眾歡迎！《死侍2》(Deadpool 2)前日上映優先場，票房輕鬆就超過200萬，以三級片來講真係好難得！由男神賴恩雷諾士(Ryan Reynolds)飾演的死侍今集繼續發揮其賤嘴本色，嘲笑對手DC的角色之餘，今次就連同公司的X-Men都成為了被玩對象！在美國權威影評網「爛番茄」(Rotten Tomatoes)中，《死侍2》得到84%新鮮度的正面評價，相信今集可以再續上集的票房佳績！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B3%A4%E5%98%B4%E7%84%A1%E6%A5%B5%E9%99%90-%E6%AD%BB%E4%BE%8D2-%E5%84%AA%E5%85%88%E5%A0%B4%E7%A5%A8%E6%88%BF%E8%BC%95%E9%AC%86%E9%81%8E200%E8%90%AC-040000637.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%25B3%25A4%25E5%2598%25B4%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E9%2599%2590-%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BE%258D2-%25E5%2584%25AA%25E5%2585%2588%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E6%2588%25BF%25E8%25BC%2595%25E9%25AC%2586%25E9%2581%258E200%25E8%2590%25AC-040000637.html&d=mEyK4i52j5nGS%2BFZh4gAfgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=ddf65652\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B3%A4%E5%98%B4%E7%84%A1%E6%A5%B5%E9%99%90-%E6%AD%BB%E4%BE%8D2-%E5%84%AA%E5%85%88%E5%A0%B4%E7%A5%A8%E6%88%BF%E8%BC%95%E9%AC%86%E9%